==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polyphonist
<hw>Po*lyph"o*nist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
proficient in the art of multiplying sounds; a ventriloquist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>A master of polyphony; a
contrapuntist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polyphonous</ent>⟦br⟧
